dct_description_sm: Depths shown by soundings and isolines; relief by contours and spot heights.
Bar scales on map in "Sea Miles," "Yards," and "Metres."
Shows reefs, shoals, vegetation, drainage, coastal relief, city plan, various facilities.
Textual descriptions, such as "Strewn with coarse dead coral," and "old fence."
Map primarily in English; responsibility, publication, etc. in Japanese; title and map information in Japanese and English.
Japan Hydrographic Department seal in upper left margin.
Date published taken from bottom margin: "昭和15年."
